keyFacts: This is a transcription request form from the DOJ OIG Investigations Division for case number 2019010614.
The form requests transcription of an audio interview recorded on September 29, 2021, with a duration of 2 hours, 12 minutes, and 15 seconds.
The subject of the interview is not named on the form; only a case agent's last name (possibly 'BAO') and a duty station are partially visible.
The form was digitally approved by an OFFICE SAC/ASAC on September 30, 2021.
The document is administrative in nature, detailing procedures for submitting transcription requests within the DOJ OIG.
